Maintainer: Nick McKay <nick@nau.edu>
Description: Ensemble methods and calculations for time-uncertain
    paleogeoscientific data, including binning, correlation, regression,
    principal component analysis, and spectral analysis across age
    ensembles, plus utilities for extracting and mapping ensembles in
    LiPD (Linked Paleo Data) objects. Split out of the 'geoChronR'
    package.
